definitions.definition: A failure to function in an expected or complete manner. Usually refers to a disorder in a bodily organ (e.g. erectile dysfunction ), a mental disorder, or the improper behavior of a social group.

main_definition: ( chiefly medicine ) A failure to function in an expected or complete manner. Usually refers to a disorder in a bodily organ (e.g. erectile dysfunction ), a mental disorder, or the improper behavior of a social group.
